divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting on my couch and heard a loud rumbling. I looked out my back window and saw 5 ships all aligned horizontal moving very slow and about 35 feet off the ground. In just a few seconds they disappeared behind the tree line which is about 200 yards from where I was watching.
Summary: 5 ships very close to each other.
